OL,3,CAnn Widdecombe murder investigation:
OL,4,CWhat we know so far
OL,6,FA murder investigation has been
OL,7,Flaunched following the death of former
OL,8,Fminister and MP Ann Widdecombe.
OL,10,FThe 78-year-old former politician was
OL,11,Ffound dead at her home on Dartmoor,
OL,12,Fand detectives say a 26-year-old man
OL,13,Fhas now been arrested on suspicion of
OL,14,Fmurder.
OL,16,FDevon and Cornwall Police said the
OL,17,Finvestigation is moving at a
OL,18,F"significant pace" - so what do we
OL,19,Fknow so far?
OL,21,FWho is Anne Widdecombe?
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/8
