OL,3,CAnn Widdecombe murder investigation:
OL,4,CWhat we know so far
OL,6,FWiddecombe was a Conservative MP
OL,7,Fbetween 1987 and 2010 for the Kent
OL,8,Fconstituency of Maidstone, later
OL,9,FMaidstone and the Weald, and held
OL,10,Fseveral ministerial positions in Sir
OL,11,FJohn Major's government.
OL,13,FShe later became a Brexit Party MEP
OL,14,Fand played a "decisive role" in
OL,15,Fgetting the UK out of the European
OL,16,FUnion, according to Nigel Farage.
OL,26,@vD@NOUvD@\O]
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/8
