OL,3,CAnn Widdecombe murder investigation:
OL,4,CWhat we know so far
OL,6,FHow did she die?
OL,8,FDevon and Cornwall Police said
OL,9,Fofficers were called to an address in
OL,10,FHaytor, Dartmoor, at 11.40am on
OL,11,FThursday 9 July, and found Miss
OL,12,FWiddecombe dead, having sustained
OL,13,F"serious injuries".
OL,15,FThey did not specify where those
OL,16,Finjuries were.
OL,18,FThere is currently a heavy police
OL,19,Fpresence outside her home, including
OL,20,Fforensic teams.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/8
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
