OL,3,CAnn Widdecombe murder investigation:
OL,4,CWhat we know so far
OL,6,FDetective Chief Inspector Ilona Rosson
OL,7,Fsaid: "This is an extremely tragic
OL,8,Fincident, and our thoughts are very
OL,9,Fmuch with the family and friends of
OL,10,FAnn Widdecombe at this difficult time.
OL,12,F"Our murder inquiry is in its early
OL,13,Fstages but moving at a significant
OL,14,Fpace. We are deploying all of the
OL,15,Fnecessary resources to find out
OL,16,Fexactly what has happened."
OL,18,FWhat do we know about the police
OL,19,Finvestigation?
OL,26,@oD@GOUtD@AOU
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/8
