PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F404A1783945155
OL,3,CAnn Widdecombe murder investigation:
OL,4,CWhat we know so far
OL,6,FA 26-year-old man was arrested on
OL,7,FFriday afternoon at an address in
OL,8,FNewton Abbot on suspicion of her
OL,9,Fmurder.
OL,11,FThe suspect is a white British
OL,12,Fnational. He is in police custody
OL,13,Fwhile enquiries continue.
OL,15,FAsked if the suspect was known to the
OL,16,Fvictim, Devon and Cornwall Police's
OL,17,FAssistant Chief Constable Matt Longman
OL,18,Fssaid they remain "open-minded"
OL,19,Fthroughout the investigation, and they
OL,20,Fare still investigating.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G6/8
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
