PN,40407
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F404A1783945155
OL,3,CAnn Widdecombe murder investigation:
OL,4,CWhat we know so far
OL,6,FThe murder inquiry is in its early
OL,7,Fstages and police are appealing to the
OL,8,Fpublic to share relevant information.
OL,10,FIs the death being treated as
OL,11,Fterrorism?
OL,13,FLongman said Widdecombe's death was
OL,14,Fnot being treated as a terrorist
OL,15,Fincident.
OL,17,FHe told reporters: "At this time, I
OL,18,Fhave got no information to believe
OL,19,Fthat that is a politically motivated
OL,20,Fcrime."
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G7/8
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
