PN,40408
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F404A1783945155
OL,3,CAnn Widdecombe murder investigation:
OL,4,CWhat we know so far
OL,6,F"While we work closely with our
OL,7,Fpartners and consulted counter-
OL,8,Fterrorism policing as part of our
OL,9,Finitial inquiries, the incident is not
OL,10,Fbeing treated as terrorism.
OL,12,F"A cordon remains in place at the
OL,13,Fproperty, while specialist officers
OL,14,Fcontinue forensic examinations. There
OL,15,Fare road closures in place around the
OL,16,Fscene, and the public will see
OL,17,Fsignificant police activity in the
OL,18,Farea while detectives and other
OL,19,Fofficers continue house-to-house and
OL,20,FCCTV inquiries.
OL,26,@nD@AOUtD@AOU
